---
title: Grilled Pork Chop with Jerk BBQ Sauce with Cilantro-Lime Corn and Grilled Sweet Potato
description: Even mild Caribbean Jerk spice is such a party for your mouth that we had to step up every other element of this lively dish. From cilantro-lime corn to grilled sweet potato, each colourful bite is a delight!
